text: Euston tube station is a London Underground station. It is served by the Victoria Line and both branches of the Northern line (not to be confused with nearby Euston Square tube station). It directly connects with the Euston mainline station above it. The station is in Travelcard Zone 1. == References == Category:Northern line stations Category:Victoria line stations Category:Tube stations in the London Borough of Camden Category:London Travelcard zone 1
